<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #0f172a; 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #1e293b;
            border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            padding: 40px; text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .body-content {
            padding: 40px; color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .welcome-text {
            font-size: 20px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .otp-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px dashed rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
            border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: #3b82f6;
            letter-spacing: 12px; margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 30px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px;
            background: #3b82f6; color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none; border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
        }
        .highlight { color: #3b82f6; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>CODEXUS</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="body-content">
            <p class="welcome-text">Hey <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>Ready to level up your coding journey? We're excited to have you on board! Use the secure activation code below to verify your account.</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Verification Code</p>
                <h2 class="otp-code"><%= activationCode %></h2>
            </div>

            <p>This code is valid for <span class="highlight">5 minutes</span>. If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            
            <p>See you on the other side!</p>
            <p><strong>Team Codexus</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2026 Codexus Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>If you have questions, ping us at <a href="mailto:support@codexus.com" style="color: #3b82f6;">support@codexus.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>